episodes.title: Top 10 Dark Celebrities In Scary Cults
episodes.description: Emily dives into the surprising and often unsettling affiliations of celebrities with various cults. The episode uncovers the childhood of David and Patricia Arquette within the Skymont Subud, a group viewed as a cult or commune. Emily also explores Rose McGowan's upbringing in The Family International, a cult with a controversial history. These and more stories reveal the complex intersections of fame, spirituality, and control, offering a unique glimpse into a lesser-known aspect of these celebrities' lives.
